Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.10,0:00:24.41,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因为总是在俩人独处的时光里 说不出话来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.03,0:00:33.67,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,小小的KISS 让时间就这样 停止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.38,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Need your love tonight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.83,0:00:48.73,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,与在探寻命运的瞬间 相遇的你 俩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.80,0:01:00.07,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,回想起 雪的home 你的身影 逐渐变小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:07.16,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远献给你喔 Winter Bell
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.44,0:01:11.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,窗边堆积的白雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.91,0:01:24.05,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,让我俩更加接近喔 Day by day 此时 请紧紧地抱着我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.34,0:01:30.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远献给你喔 Winter Bell
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.88,0:01:41.99,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,此时 请紧紧地抱着我 在星星降临的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.50,0:21:23.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是等待  刺激的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.70,0:21:30.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前所见的  全部是重要的所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.20,0:21:42.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,失去的东西是恐怖的  但我们之间还什么也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah　yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:50.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在这蓝蓝的地球上  无限重复未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.00,0:21:55.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,can make me free　想要感觉这种跳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.50,0:22:02.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,这个心情飞舞升起 染满天空与大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.50,0:22:12.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住你 想要飞起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.90,0:22:15.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.10,0:22:21.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,这个心情飞舞升起 染满天空与大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:31.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住你 想要飞起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏的是心中的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照耀两人的是星星和雪花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于步美的想法 暗号解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽是谜团的那家伙是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透了真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个外表看似小孩 智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看完了Paul & Annie的动物表演的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救了因被错认而被记者重重包围的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.20,0:02:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了接我们去饭店而去取车的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然失去了踪影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.00,0:02:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是留下了一个沾了血的手机链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自芝加哥的男人(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P&A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉在这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.20,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是詹姆斯先生留给我们犯人的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.60,0:02:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.30,0:02:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手机链的P和&和A都沾着血 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.80,0:02:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就回局里调查一下这是不是真正的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那明天到警察局里见呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.10,0:02:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 至少也要知道P&A的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和A会不会是PAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是做面包的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 面包店什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在紧急关头的情况下 要想传递PAN的信息的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就应该直接把P和A一起染上血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个暗号应该把P和A分开来想比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和A  P和A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉色和红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,角斗和包子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电脑和访问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手枪和暗杀者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.90,0:03:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难道是说Parking Area吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 停车场吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在哪的停车场也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.90,0:03:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.00,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说詹姆斯先生刚刚停车的停车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许还留下其他的什么线索呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚刚我也是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以先调查了一下 结果什么也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死 怎么想都不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就只能先在这周围打听一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家分开打听一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.30,0:04:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有谁看见这附近有带着外国人的两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.40,0:04:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果发现了什么的话 就用侦探徽章来联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么也找不到侦探徽章了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没掉到哪里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚给詹姆斯先生看的时候还...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 夏洛克·福尔摩斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的詹姆斯先生还拿着我的侦探徽章呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用徽章里面装的发信器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.70,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的位置是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里往北距离16公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正沿着泰晤士街道开始北上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从速度来看的话应该是汽车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是汽车吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰晤士街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了这个的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你以为你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.90,0:05:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在几门街道和崎玉县的县界之间进行盘查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭着这么模糊的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就进行盘查的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个外国人有可能会被杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呀 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在那边正好发生交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美正在进行交通疏导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要确认可疑的人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拜托给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身高大约180厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五 六十岁左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带眼镜 长胡子 操英国口音的美国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人乘坐的车子 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果发现了这辆车的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上进行调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 犯人可能携带武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和高木警官马上就过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们到晚上为止都有空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且和那个孩子有关的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象都挺有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样 我们也去 博士把车子开过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们才能确认詹姆斯先生的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有一点怀疑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生和两个男人从停车场穿过小巷到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘了另一辆车的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个血的暗号应该是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.50,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小巷里面走的时候割破自己的手指留下的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 应该是在停车场的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被两个男人用手枪什么的威胁着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后瞒着那两个男人偷偷留下的暗号吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是明知道是可疑人物还特意跟着去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并给我们留下了信息吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你想说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被别人牵着鼻子走的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想的太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚车里坐的人的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 没看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外国人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能不能让我们先过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑之前必须和这个人做现场验证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你们辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在情人的房间里胡闹的小气家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国人一个也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在车子在什么地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这前面8公里处移动中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快没电了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么从这里蒙混过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个外国人带着徽章的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.80,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接问问他现在在哪里不就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.00,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果呼叫的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有被犯人发现的危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.60,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不解开P&A之谜就不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是指车子去的目的地呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是饭和冰激凌 是饭店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是指头型 也许是美容院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.19,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能认真一点地想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水鸟和海豹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.70,0:10:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是指动物园吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生不是喜欢动物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是动物园的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沾血的地方就应该是Animal show的Animal了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生所在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.60,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人乘坐的是警车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不早一点抓到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会让他们跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美 怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到柯南所说的绑架犯了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.70,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绑架犯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南说他们坐在警车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.40,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生给我们留下的信息P&A的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是指警车的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说P&A是警车呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把P&A里的&用字母表示试着排列一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P&A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和AND和A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PANDA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是熊猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警车的颜色就是白色和黑色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这就是熊猫的原因 原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.80,0:12:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实会有日本警察把警车叫做熊猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.30,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 被绑架的应该是英籍美国人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.10,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外国人应该不会知道日本警察的行话呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是警车的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是车身带有黑白色纹的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不都象熊猫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.00,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是那时外国人能看到熊猫的书也说不定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为被绑架的詹姆斯先生是在伦敦长大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说警车是没错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.60,0:12:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前英国的警车的车身也是被涂为黑色和白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.60,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是1965年由英国警察第一次引进的叫熊猫的警车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.70,0:12:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警车就等于熊猫 这在英国人的心里已经扎根了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在英语的字典里面也有熊猫车这一说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 年轻的英国人可能不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那个时代生活过的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看见警车应该就马上会联想到熊猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时代的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚巧有一辆警车过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是车上乘坐了什么外国人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.70,0:13:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车上坐的警官 没什么可疑的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是有两名警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在嫌疑犯的头上蒙着大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在后面的座位上 把嫌疑犯夹在中间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就 就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.60,0:13:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻而易举 轻而易举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.00,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就按你的计划在日落之前到达群马县的深山里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你的完美计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要掉以轻心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得可疑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通的交通疏导警 却在一辆一辆车地检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.30,0:14:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道 我们已经暴露了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们抓错了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先用枪顶住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果等一下再有奇怪地盘查的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强行突破吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有 有点不妙啊 佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经是崎玉县了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经让崎玉县的警官进行盘查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不用特意地追查也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不担心吗 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个警车已经由由美检查了一遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果事情暴露的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.50,0:15:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就有可能会用在被盘查的时候以人质进行要挟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在由美检查的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个外国人也是一动不动的没有反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说犯罪集团持有武器的可能性相当高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,携带了手枪作武器的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被盘查的时候如果对人质不利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我就一直在想要如何使犯人在不注意地情况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们包围起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那种象魔法一样的办法能有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种办法的话 不是没有的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侦探团徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚偷偷地放在这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那个车子的后面500米的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要试一试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成功的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在于是否还有很多警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 一直跟到这个地方来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.90,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美 你在跟着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为好象是我让犯人跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.60,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美 你以前确实是做过崎玉县的监事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是 是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死 又是红灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别着急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们不张扬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不会暴露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们的天下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 不好 是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是被发现了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把人质当挡箭牌逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救 救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是总厅的高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请帮助我们抓住那个绑架犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,适当地跟在后面 然后在岔道离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 上当了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行得顺利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行得很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过不要担心了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到岔道的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么停滞不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会让犯人跑掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左面不行的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就去右面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右面另有一辆警车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面也被警车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.80,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们前后左右完全被警察包围了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得不赖嘛 侦探队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我还是叫你福尔摩斯比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就和他们拼命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有人质呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当有人一声令下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体车辆同时进行刹车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的身体倾斜的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会束手就擒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有些粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但干得很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酷小伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家了 得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 轻而易举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次的聚会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在总厅集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果佐藤警官也能来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.80,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人质詹姆斯·布兰克先生在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.30,0:19:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还在的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是很可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在进行事件调查之前失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没觉得有什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他象个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在意地只是他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.20,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为布兰克(黑)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是詹姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 是詹姆斯·邦德的詹姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 倒觉得是个好印象的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·莫里亚帝教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪界的拿破仑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,福尔摩斯的夙敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫里亚帝教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他开头的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么想的只是夏洛克罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯只是一个到处都有的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.50,0:20:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比这个更担心地是那个车里看我们的那个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.70,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是劫持公共汽车事件里的一名乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实在事件调查时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.60,0:21:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫做赤井秀一的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.70,0:22:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事前就想好留下了那个暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.40,0:22:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是假警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.90,0:22:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们对我就好象是理所当然得说了日语的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们作为警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.70,0:22:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是知道我是能说日语的外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始也应该至少确认一下姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们明明知道我是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.30,0:23:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却假装不知道来接近我的可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 好象是弄错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.80,0:23:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.90,0:23:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却大吃一惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.20,0:23:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把那么长的头发一下子剪短了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改头换面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被恋人狠狠地甩掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.70,0:23:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是为此特意地把我叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.60,0:23:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想和恋人重归于好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.30,0:23:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要让她后悔 把我甩掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.70,0:23:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用血和泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.10,0:23:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个血迹是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害啊 今天没睡觉就能推理出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.50,0:24:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 这个手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.70,0:24:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.40,0:24:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摇动的餐厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.70,0:24:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.10,0:24:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼鳞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次 是不可思议的餐馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.50,0:24:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论点什么 只会来鳗鱼饭 啊 很好的餐厅吧
